    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>We have flagship areas of expertise in <strong>health and rehabilitation</strong>, <strong>sustainable business</strong> and <strong>creativity and culture</strong>. Like all our teaching, research and knowledge exchange work, the outputs of our flagship areas are designed to be thoroughly relevant to society’s needs. </p>]]></Value>
